## You spoke, we listened
Do you find current CORE confusing and tricky to use? Is it the last thing your team wants to do? We’ve taken some of your biggest pain points and created solutions to make submitting data simpler.

For example, you told us that current CORE often rejects postcodes. Now we accept all postcodes, even for new-build properties - so you can complete your logs faster.

We’ve also made sure the rent ranges reflect real-life examples, and made it easier for you to spot any mistakes. This means you can submit accurate data first time, with less help from us.
